thread.title: Robert R.

author: Robert R.
title: Robert R.
text: I ordered my safe and they were up on communication, letting me know every step of the way until it shipped. Once shipped I got the tracking number and was able to track it. It arrived safe(no pun intended) and sound and I already set it up and placed my weapons in it. I'm happy with my purchase and will look to them again if my needs change safe wise.
